# Oracle Bull — routing for a prerendered (SSG) + SPA hybrid.
#
# WHY THIS FILE MATTERS FOR SEO:
# The static host serves exact file paths (e.g. /dashboard/index.html) but does
# NOT, on its own, map a clean URL like /dashboard to /dashboard/index.html.
# Previously the only rule was "/*  /index.html  200", so EVERY clean URL fell
# through to the homepage shell — and the homepage's <link rel="canonical" href="/">
# told Google that all ~2469 pages were duplicates of the homepage. Result: only
# the homepage could index; every prediction/market/compare/learn page was dropped.
#
# The rules below rewrite each clean URL to its prerendered index.html (status 200
# = serve in place, NOT a redirect) BEFORE the SPA fallback. Section patterns use
# :splat so they cover any depth (coin, timeframe, year, q-page) and auto-include
# future coins without edits. Auth/app routes (/my/*, /trade, /admin) match none of
# these and correctly fall through to the SPA shell for client-side routing.
#
# Order matters: most specific first, "/*  /index.html" MUST stay last.

# ── Dynamic content sections (any depth via :splat) ────────────────────────────
/airdrops/*          /airdrops/:splat/index.html          200
/chain/*             /chain/:splat/index.html             200
/compare/*           /compare/:splat/index.html           200
/factory/*           /factory/:splat/index.html           200
/how-to-buy/*        /how-to-buy/:splat/index.html        200
/insights/*          /insights/:splat/index.html          200
/learn/*             /learn/:splat/index.html             200
/liquidations/*      /liquidations/:splat/index.html      200
/market/*            /market/:splat/index.html            200
/price-prediction/*  /price-prediction/:splat/index.html  200
/q/*                 /q/:splat/index.html                 200
/tools/*             /tools/:splat/index.html             200

# ── Single hub / leaf pages (clean URL -> its prerendered index.html) ──────────
/about                  /about/index.html                  200
/advertise              /advertise/index.html              200
